<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Withdrawal Request Received – FundingHero</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
      margin:0; 
      padding:20px; 
      background:#f5f5f5; 
      color:#333; 
    }
    .email-container { 
      max-width:400px; 
      margin:0 auto; 
      background:#fff; 
      padding:20px; 
      border-radius:8px; 
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .banner { 
      width:100%; 
      height:auto; 
      border-radius:8px 8px 0 0; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
    }
    .title { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:24px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      margin-bottom:30px; 
    }
    .user-greeting { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:18px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
    }
    .main-message { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:16px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
    }
    .description { 
      color:#666; 
      font-size:14px; 
      line-height:1.4; 
      margin-bottom:15px; 
    }
    .withdrawal-box { 
      background:#fff; 
      padding:15px; 
      border-radius:6px; 
      border:2px solid #E6B800; 
      margin:20px 0; 
    }
    .highlight { 
      color:#E6B800; 
      font-weight:bold; 
    }
    .status-info { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:14px; 
      margin-bottom:8px; 
    }
    .amount-highlight { 
      color:#B8860B; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      font-size:18px; 
    }
    .action-button { 
      background:#E6B800; 
      color:#fff; 
      padding:12px 20px; 
      border:none; 
      border-radius:6px; 
      font-size:16px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      width:100%; 
      margin:20px 0; 
      text-align:center; 
      text-decoration:none; 
      display:block; 
      cursor:pointer; 
      box-sizing:border-box; 
    }
    .action-button:hover { 
      background:#B8860B; 
    }
    .steps { 
      background:#fff; 
      padding:15px; 
      border-radius:6px; 
      border:2px solid #E6B800; 
      margin:20px 0; 
    }
    .steps-title { 
      color:#B8860B; 
      font-size:14px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      margin-bottom:10px; 
    }
    .steps-list { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:12px; 
      line-height:1.4; 
    }
    .footer-text { 
      color:#666; 
      font-size:12px; 
      margin-top:20px; 
    }
    .copyright { 
      color:#999; 
      font-size:11px; 
      margin-top:15px; 
      text-align:center; 
    }
    .company-name { 
      color:#E6B800; 
      font-weight:bold; 
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="FundingHero Banner" class="banner">
    
    <div class="title">Withdrawal Request Received</div>
    
    <div class="user-greeting">Hello {{firstName}} {{lastName}}</div>
    
    <div class="main-message">Your withdrawal request is being processed</div>
    
    <div class="description">
      We have successfully received your withdrawal request. Our team is processing your request and you'll receive your funds soon.
    </div>
    
    <div class="withdrawal-box">
      <div class="status-info"><strong>Trader:</strong> <span class="highlight">{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</span></div>
      <div class="status-info"><strong>Email:</strong> <span class="highlight">{{correo}}</span></div>
      <div class="status-info"><strong>Account Size:</strong> <span class="highlight">${{account_size}}</span></div>
      <div class="status-info"><strong>Withdrawal Amount:</strong> <span class="amount-highlight">${{amount}}</span></div>
      <div class="status-info"><strong>Percentage:</strong> <span class="highlight">{{percentaje}}%</span></div>
      <div class="status-info"><strong>Wallet:</strong> <span class="highlight">{{wallet}}</span></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="steps-title">Next steps:</div>
      <div class="steps-list">
        1. Our team will review your withdrawal request<br>
        2. We'll verify your account and trading history<br>
        3. Once approved, funds will be processed to your wallet<br>
        4. You'll receive confirmation once transfer is complete
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="description">
      You can monitor the status of your withdrawal request at any time through your dashboard.
    </div>
    
    <a href="{{landingUrl}}" class="action-button" target="_blank">View Dashboard</a>
    
    <div class="description">
      <span class="highlight">Thank you for your patience!</span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer-text">
      Best regards,<br><br>
      <span class="company-name">FundingHero</span> Team
    </div>
    
    <div class="copyright">
      © 2025 <span class="company-name">FundingHero</span>. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>